    "description": "Put your reflexes to the ultimate test with this brand new, unique arcade-style endless runner: Warp speed: Infinity. Save your colony by making your way through space at incredible speeds while dodging a huge variety of; asteroids, ice crystals, wrecks and other space junk. Unlock a variety of different ships with unique features and handling. Fly through gas bubbles to alter your velocity to break your personal record. The higher your score gets, the more ships you'll unlock. <br><br>Combining simplicity with extremely challenging gameplay, Warp speed Infinity allows anyone to play one of the hardest games in existence with no prior knowledge of the game or its controls. Unlocking all the ships is challenging but completing the game is almost impossible.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010320/extras/dfea47dcfae3c92251879f1388041ea3.avif?t=1719775921\" width=540 height=564 /></span>",
